responses.body:
{
  "run": {
    "destination_name": "",
    "direction_id": {{faker 'number.int' max=99999}},
    "express_stop_count": {{faker 'number.int' max=99999}},
    "final_stop_id": {{faker 'number.int' max=99999}},
    "geopath": [
      {}
    ],
    "route_id": {{faker 'number.int' max=99999}},
    "route_type": {{faker 'number.int' max=99999}},
    "run_id": {{faker 'number.int' max=99999}},
    "run_ref": "",
    "run_sequence": {{faker 'number.int' max=99999}},
    "status": "",
    "vehicle_descriptor": {
      "air_conditioned": {{faker 'datatype.boolean'}},
      "description": "",
      "id": "",
      "length": "",
      "low_floor": {{faker 'datatype.boolean'}},
      "operator": "",
      "supplier": ""
    },
    "vehicle_position": {
      "bearing": {{faker 'number.float'}},
      "datetime_utc": "{{faker 'date.recent' 365}}",
      "direction": "",
      "easting": {{faker 'number.float'}},
      "expiry_time": "{{faker 'date.recent' 365}}",
      "latitude": {{faker 'number.float'}},
      "longitude": {{faker 'number.float'}},
      "northing": {{faker 'number.float'}},
      "supplier": ""
    }
  },
  "status": {
    "health": "{{oneOf (array '0' '1')}}",
    "version": ""
  }
}
responses.label: The trip/service run details for the run_ref and route type specified.
